Jesus died for you! He loves you more than you can fathom! Due to Covid-19 we are endeavoring to follow Provincial guidlines for our services. We will be holding in person services at 10:30 am in the fellowship hall following a board approved protocol. Sunday July 26, 2020 10:30 am Worship Service - In the Church Hall - doors open at 10:15 am. Sunday August 2, 2020 No Service Sunday August 9, 2020 10:30 am Worship Service - In Church Hall - doors open at 10:15 am. Please be aware that these announcements could change! Please call the church voicemail 905-899-1373 to be assured the services are still happening.﻿ ﻿ God of Light and Love, We pray....... Our Mission To be a faithful growing church, that demonstrates true community, deep Christian spirituality and a passion for justice. Micah 6:8﻿﻿ ﻿ Our Vision To be and to share the Good News of Jesus Christ, witnessing, loving and serving from our doorsteps "to the ends of the earth." Acts 1:8 Winger's﻿ Mission ﻿﻿"To bring people to the Lord by actively promoting the living Gospel of the redeeming love of God through our Saviour Jesus Christ." ﻿ ﻿ ﻿ ﻿ Copyright 2009 Winger Church of Christ (Disciples). All rights reserved. Web Hosting by Yahoo! 43238 Hwy 3 P.O. 53 Wainfleet, ON L0S 1V0 ph: 905-899-1373 wingerdisciples@yahoo.ca
